snippet.title: WiLD Gameplay Trailer - Paris Games Week 2015 (PS4 gameplay)
snippet.description:
Ride a bear! Be a rabbit! Fly around a bit as an eagle! Something about a snake lady!

All this and more in the new WiLD gameplay trailer from Paris Games Week. It's looking lovely, isn't it?
